---
title: Breaded Crispy Chicken and Garlic Rice with Peas and Marinara Sauce
description: This Breaded Crispy Chicken and Garlic Rice is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
